Vo ngy 10/9/2019, Apple  chnh thc tung ra dng sn phm iPhone 11 series. N gm tng cng l 3 phin bn  l: iPhone 11 thng v 2 model cao cp l iPhone 11 Pro v iPhone 11 Pro Max.
D  tri qua nhiu nm t ngy ra mt, iPhone 11 c series vn tip tc thu ht ngi dng bi nhng li th ring bit nh sau:
- Mang trong mnh con chip <font style="color: rgb(236, 120, 120);">A13 </font>Bionic mnh m, cc mu iPhone 11 like new vn p ng tt cc tc v v gii tr m khng gp kh khn v hiu sut nh tr hnh hay git lag.
- H thng camera sc nt v kh nng quay video 4K 60fps mang n nhng bc nh v video cht lng cao xn s.

- C mc gi cnh tranh v bn di hn so vi nhiu mu in thoi Android nn va uy tn m li va c cht lng cao.

<font style="color: rgb(0, 188, 212);">Ngy nay, cc model iPhone 11 likenew c phn chia thnh ch yu l 4 loi khc nhau. S c ring tng yu t  phn loi v ng nhin gi thnh ca chng cng s c s khc bit. Di y chnh l chi tit  khch hng tham kho.</font>

iPhone 11 c loi chnh hng Apple l nhng thit b c<font style="color: rgb(236, 120, 120);"> hng phn phi ring</font> ti th trng Vit Namvi m my kt thc bng VN/A. Do , ngi dng khi chn mua sn phm loi ny khng phi ln tn nhiu bi bn s c s hu mt in thoi gn nh mi vi v ngoi tuyt p. Tuy nhin, hin loi hng ny ca iPhone 11 likenew khng cn nhiu bi Apple khng cn sn xut n na.

iPhone 11 s hu hiu nng kh mnh m, n nh trong thi gian di nh c trang b chipset A13 Bionic. Mn hnh LCD 6.1 inch sc nt cng cht lng hin th Full HD ca my cho tri nghim hnh nh mt m v c tng phn cao. H thng camera hin i c tch hp nhng tnh nng cng ngh mi kt hp vi vin Pin dung lng 3110mAh, gip nng cao tri nghim ca ngi dng.

D iPhone 11 l mt trong nhng thit b smartphone tm trung ng mua nht  thi im hin ti, bn cng nn cn thn la chn dng sn phm ny chnh hng VN/A  c c tri nghim tt nht. Nhiu ngi v ham r m  chn mua phi dng iPhone 11 km cht lng, khng phi hng chnh hng VN/A, dn ti hiu qu s dng thp, khng p ng c cc nhu cu cng vic, gii tr.

Mt trong nhng l do m bn nn mua dng sn phm iPhone 11 chnh hng ny l bn s nhn c ch  bo hnh chnh hng 12 thng ti cc trung tm bo hnh u quyn ca Apple ti Vit Nam. y l c quyn m ch cc sn phm chnh hng VN/A nhn c. Nhiu dng sn phm iPhone xch tay t Hn Quc, Nht Bn v cc nc khc u khng nhn c ch bo hnh chnh hng ny ti Vit Nam.

Bn cnh , cht lng ca cc sn phm chnh hng VN/A cng c m bo hn cc dng sn phm khng r ngun gc v cc sn phm xch tay ti t cc quc gia khc. Cc thng s k thut ca cc sn phm VN/A u  c hiu chnh chi tit  m bo c c  bn b, chc chn nht ti tng quc gia c th m  y l Vit Nam.

So vi iPhone XR th siu phm Apple nm 2019 c nhiu nng cp ng gi, trong  ni bt l con chip x l, b nh RAM, dung lng pin, c bit l camera trc v sau. Di y l bng so snh thng s k thut ca iPhone 11 v XR bn c th tham kho:
Trong ln ra mt ny, iPhone 11  rt c Apple u i khi s hu ti tn 6 phin bn mu khc nhau ln lt l: Trng, , en, Xanh Mint, Tm v Vng. y u l nhng phin bn mu c bit tot ln c s sang trng, qu phi ca ngi s dng.
